tafsir[15]{c,v,t}:
  15,1,"Alif, laam, raa: yewtere fii sugu ɗee Aayeeje yawtiino ka arannde cortewol(simoore) Baqarah. Ɗee Aayeeje ko mawnuɗe fiyaaku, tinndinɗe wonnde ko ɗe jippiniaaɗe ka Alla, Aayeeje Alqur'aana ɓannginɗe tawhiidi e sari'aaji."
  15,2,"Heeferɓe ɓen yeloyto Ñalnde Darngal, tuma feeñanta ɓe meere keeferaaku ngu ɓe wonunoo e mun aduna, sinno ɓe laatino juulɓe."
  15,3,"An Nulaaɗo, accu ɓee fennooɓe ñaamira no neemoraaɗi ñaamirta, ɓe dakmitora dakamme aduna lannayɗe, ɓe sokolira juutingol caate gaa gomɗinal e golle moƴƴe. Aray ɓe annda ko ɓe wonunoo e hayrere kon, tuma ɓe darnoyaa yeeso Alla Ñalnde Darngal."
  15,4,"Men jippinaali halkaare e saare jeyaande e tooñunde, si wanaa hara no woodani nde lajal dot-tangal anndaangal ka Alla, ngal ɓeydotaako ngal ɗuytotaako."
  15,5,"Mofte woo halketaake ado lajal majje timmude, ɗe nennantaake ɗum kadi si hewtii. Haani hara tooñooɓe ɓen ɗaynitoraali ko Alla nennitirani ɓe kon."
  15,6,"Heeferɓe makka ɓen wi'ani Nulaaɗo Alla on (yo o his): Ko an yo nodditiiɗo jippineede e mun (Deftere nden), pellet aan e noddugol maa ko a kaangaaɗo haɗa firlito pirlitagol feetuɗo."
  15,7,"Ko haɗ Ma addande amen Malaykaaji ɗi ceedo wonde ko a goonɗuɗo e nelal ma he e tellagol lepte."
  15,8,"Alla jaaborii ƴamol maɓɓe addugol Malaa'ika ngol: Men jippinirtaa Malaa'ika si wanaa ko yahdata e ñeenñal, tuma hewti halkirgol ɓe lepte. Ɓe wonoy- tah, tuma Men addoyta Malaa'ika, hara ɓe gomɗi- naali, leelnoyteeɓe, ko woni, ɓe yacciniroyte lepte ɗen."
  15,9,"Ko Menen woni ko jippini ndee Alqur'aanaare e fonndo Muhammadu (jom-kisiyee) siftinore yimɓe ɓen. Menen kadi ko Men reenooɓe nde e ɓeydee- de maa ɗuyteede, maa walylee, waɗtitee."
  15,10,"Gomɗii Men nuliino ado maa an Nulaaɗo, Nulaaɓe goo, e leñi yeddunooɓe ko adii, ɓe fenni ɓe. Wanaa an adaa fenneede e Nulaaɓe ɓen."
  15,11,"Nulaaɗo woo araali e ɗen mofte heeferɓe adinooɓe, si wanaa ɓe fennay mo ɓe jalkita."
  15,12,"Ko wano Men naadirnoo fennugol ngol e ɓerɗe ɗen mofte, Men naadirta ɗum e ɓerɗe sirkooɓe Makka ɓen, sabu ɗuurnagol ɓe townitoo ngol."
  15,13,"Ɓe gomɗintaa ndee Alqur'aanaare jippinaande e Muhammadu (yo o his), gomɗii sunna Alla on e halkugol fennuɓe Nulaaɓe mun ɓen yawtiino. Yo fennooɓe ma ɓen waajito."
  15,14,"Ɓee fennooɓe townitiiɓe, hay goonga kan feeñirani ɓe hujjaaji ɓannguɗi, hay Men udditanno ɓe damal ka kammu, ɓe waɗti ƴawrude."
  15,15,"Ɓe goongintaano, ɓe wi'ayno : Anndee gite amen ɗen hippa e yi'ugol. Wurin ko men yi'aynoo ko batte mbilewu, ko men mbilaa ɓe."